  <summary date="2019-08-23T16:35:09Z" status="Introduced in House">Untraceable Firearms Act of 2018

This bill generally prohibits and penalizes the manufacture, sale, transfer, purchase, or receipt of a ghost gun. A ghost gun is a firearm that lacks a unique serial number.</summary>
